{"id":4030,"date":"2019-01-30T14:44:07","date_gmt":"2019-01-30T14:44:07","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=4030"},"modified":"2021-02-27T03:47:06","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T03:47:06","slug":"mang-mau-trong-phong-cach-noi-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/mang-mau-trong-phong-cach-noi-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u trong Phong c\u00e1ch N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u0111a h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n. K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trung t\u00ednh n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u \u0111\u1eadm. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ba m\u00e0u trong m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i: m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u n\u1ec1n, m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u nh\u1ea5n.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5589\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/9da7ef72509089.5bea008737b32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/9da7ef72509089.5bea008737b32.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/9da7ef72509089.5bea008737b32-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/9da7ef72509089.5bea008737b32-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/9da7ef72509089.5bea008737b32-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>M\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, kh\u01a1i d\u1eady x\u00fac c\u1ea3m b\u00ecnh y\u00ean v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c sang tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf m\u00e0u s\u1eafc l\u00e0m n\u00ean t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n, h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng gian ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac. D\u1ea3i m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh lan t\u1ecfa r\u1ed9ng kh\u1eafp v\u00e0 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e0 c\u00f2n cho ph\u00e9p chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u, b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 h\u01a1i \u1ea5m c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5590\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a5f3ab72509089.5beac66389b3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"933\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a5f3ab72509089.5beac66389b3a.jpg 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a5f3ab72509089.5beac66389b3a-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a5f3ab72509089.5beac66389b3a-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/a5f3ab72509089.5beac66389b3a-1024x682.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh (m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng, m\u00e0u be, n\u00e2u, \u0111en). Ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u theo t\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh kh\u1ed1i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u1ea1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 g\u00f2 b\u00f3 khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trong phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng gam m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o gi\u00fap mang l\u1ea1i rung c\u1ea3m v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ecb gi\u00e1c. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u1eddng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 d\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 4 m\u00e0u, h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 3 m\u00e0u v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 h\u00f2a tr\u1ed9n 60-30-10: 60% m\u00e0u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o, 30% m\u00e0u trung gian v\u00e0 10% m\u00e0u nh\u1ea5n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5591\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/8d4c3375996649.5c5c66d211106.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"859\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/8d4c3375996649.5c5c66d211106.png 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/8d4c3375996649.5c5c66d211106-300x184.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/8d4c3375996649.5c5c66d211106-768x471.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/8d4c3375996649.5c5c66d211106-1024x628.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc theo phong c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u01b0\u1ee3t ngo\u00e0i s\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 h\u1ec7 m\u00e0u m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m trung t\u00e2m, &nbsp;h\u1ec7 m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u v\u00e0ng, da cam l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1o, h\u1ec7 m\u00e0u c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n v\u1edbi m\u00e0u ph\u1ea5n trang nh\u00e3 hay h\u1ec7 m\u00e0u m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng s\u1eafc h\u1ed3ng d\u1ecbu\u2026 D\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ec7 m\u00e0u n\u00e0o \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t, h\u00e0i h\u00f2a, ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ch\u1ec9nh th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc theo \u0111\u1eb7c th\u00f9 t\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng gian.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-5592\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/c6fbe075996649.5c5c66d211ac9.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"859\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/c6fbe075996649.5c5c66d211ac9.png 1400w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/c6fbe075996649.5c5c66d211ac9-300x184.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/c6fbe075996649.5c5c66d211ac9-768x471.png 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/c6fbe075996649.5c5c66d211ac9-1024x628.png 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" \/><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">M\u00e0u s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1ea3ng m\u00e0u trong phong c\u00e1ch n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u00e0u trung t\u00ednh nh\u1eb1m t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t ph\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec7m cho c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng trang tr\u00ed b\u00ean trong, h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n quan tr\u1ecdng. N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t v\u00e0 m\u1ea3ng kh\u1ed1i. V\u00ec v\u1eady n\u1ebfu b\u00e0n gh\u1ebf, k\u1ec7 TV hay t\u1ee7 b\u1ebfp&#8230; nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u00e0u \u0111\u1eadm, mang t\u00ednh t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n cao, th\u00ec n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0u s\u00e1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eafng, s\u1eefa, ghi&#8230; V\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng trong nh\u00e0, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u01b0a th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf t\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3n c\u0169ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a c\u00e1c m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u01a1n s\u1eafc, m\u00e0u trang nh\u00e3, thay v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u hoa v\u0103n, h\u1ecda ti\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u1ecf, b\u1edfi n\u00f3 gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u0111a h\u00f3a kh\u00f4ng gian v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng h\u01a1n. K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c d\u1ea1ng h\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u00e1o b\u1ea1o, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trung t\u00ednh&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5589,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4030","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4030","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v